  <brief_title>Effects of Fortified Complementary Foods on Vitamin A Status and Body Pool Size in Ghanaian Infants.</brief_title>
  <acronym>vitapool</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomised Controlled Home-based Trial of the Effects of Fortified Complementary Foods on Vitamin A Status and Body Pool Size in Ghanaian Infants.</official_title>
